OL,3,CFlooding forces closure of Moffat
OL,4,CAcademy
OL,6,FA secondary school in southern
OL,7,FScotland has been forced to close
OL,8,Ffollowing damage caused by flooding.
OL,10,FMoffat Academy has been shut by
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway Council after
OL,12,Fwhat has been described as "major
OL,13,Fwater ingress" on both floors of the
OL,14,Fbuilding.
OL,16,FThe school, which is one of 17
OL,17,Fsecondary schools in the councils
OL,18,Fcatchment area, has a roll of about
OL,19,F250 pupils.
