OL,6,FThe secondary had been closed to all
OL,7,Fyear groups due to the water damage
OL,8,Fthat was discovered on around 8am on
OL,9,FMonday 27 May.
OL,11,FParent and pupils have been reassured
OL,12,Fthat scheduled exams for S4, S5 and S6
OL,13,Fwill run as planned on Tuesday 28 May.
