OL,3,CFlooding forces closure of Moffat
OL,4,CAcademy
OL,6,FIt is thought that an issue arose due
OL,7,Fto a leak in a water purification
OL,8,Fmachine used to make de-ionised water
OL,9,Ffor experiments. This caused
OL,10,Fsignificant flooding affecting various
OL,11,Frooms within the building as well as
OL,12,Fdamage to ICT equipment, coursework
OL,13,Fand resources.JSteven Kirkpatrick,
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway Council, said:
OL,15,F"Progress has been made with the clean
OL,16,Fup throughout today, however water
OL,17,Fstill seems to be seeping through some
OL,18,Fceilings and under some walls between
OL,19,Fclassrooms.
