OL,4,CAcademy
OL,6,F"We are continuing to assess and carry
OL,7,Fout checks on equipment such as fire
OL,8,Fsensors to ensure they are working
OL,9,Fcorrectly and have not been affected
OL,10,Fby the flood water."
OL,12,FMoffat's nursery and primary school
OL,13,Fremain unaffected.
OL,15,FIt is expected that the secondary
OL,16,Fschool building will remain closed
OL,17,Funtil Wednesday 29 May.
